title: Kevin Kendle - Clouds [FLAC]
description:
Listening to Kevin Kendle's beautiful musical interpretations of cloud formations is a relaxing and therapeutic as actually lying in the sun-drenched meadow watching the clouds drift by. Kevin is a master of the keyboard to almost magical effect - guitars, saxophone, strings, voices, flutes and many other sounds are all combined to create a vast, timeless soundscape. Just listen to the music and lose yourself in its gentle beauty.
